{"tid":540642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB錯誤報道浸大「校友」聯署　懷疑造假資料　","createTime":"2018-01-25T16:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T15:11:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":142,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0c88d5b0ea5f5523ab981458501a08645b82863c","tid":540642,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"無線新聞錯誤報道浸大校友聯署　懷疑造假資料　有違傳媒基本操守<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/211961842699062/permalink/212307199331193/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F211961842699062%2Fpermalink%2F212307199331193%2F&d=yZt%2BeEGgbzpLDrv0YPSTxY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=1cd6f15d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/211961842699062/permalink/212307199331193/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/27072422_10156133478588223_3269959665369066925_n.jpg?oh=8efeea04ccc8968251160508cc58627a&amp;oe=5AF64C7F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F27072422_10156133478588223_3269959665369066925_n.jpg%3Foh%3D8efeea04ccc8968251160508cc58627a%26oe%3D5AF64C7F&h=4ddcafa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26907578_10156133478578223_6174529735375076692_n.jpg?oh=53dd078567a9f8dce5c76af49d2b49be&amp;oe=5AF56CC0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26907578_10156133478578223_6174529735375076692_n.jpg%3Foh%3D53dd078567a9f8dce5c76af49d2b49be%26oe%3D5AF56CC0&h=a7c75e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26993236_10156133478573223_7833265854416803663_n.jpg?oh=f796cdc8af22203a23296dd72180e549&amp;oe=5AE5F4CE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26993236_10156133478573223_7833265854416803663_n.jpg%3Foh%3Df796cdc8af22203a23296dd72180e549%26oe%3D5AE5F4CE&h=96da7c14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先，感謝各浸大校友的支持，在我們公開聲明要求浸大校方撤回兩位同學的處分後，已有超過400名校友參與聯署。同時，亦有一些傳媒報道是次聯署。這顯示校友有一定的集體力量，可向校方施壓，阻止不公義的校政，並讓社會知道我們的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n可是，我們發現其中無綫新聞涉嫌造假新聞，錯誤報道有關校友聯署的訊息。無綫新聞網頁版於今日（1月25日）下午6時30分左右發放題為「浸大生辱罵教師事件 陳樂行下月中接受紀律聆訊」的影像及文字報道，當中有一句寫道：「另外，有校友發起聯署支持校長錢大康，認為真正教育要獎懲並用。」而報道員在新聞錄像中讀到這一句時，畫面顯示的是一個名為「HKG報」的臉書群組所發起的一個聯署。<br />\n<br />\n翻查「HKG報」的臉書，我們發現這個所謂「支持錢大康」的聯署，並沒有說明是由浸大校友所發起的。<br />\n<br />\n我們早於今日下午1時50分左右將我們的聲明及聯署網頁電郵至無綫新聞部，但一直未獲回覆，亦未發現無綫新聞有報道我們的聯署行動。<br />\n<br />\n直至今日晚上7時，我們仍然未見到有任何一個網上聯署是以浸大校友為名支持錢大康校長或校方的處分決定。<br />\n<br />\n我們在此呼籲各校友、同學，及市民，小心留意網上訊息，勿要被騙徒、違背道德的傳媒，及帶有政治目的的人士誤導。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源<br />\n<br />\n無綫新聞：浸大生辱罵教師事件 陳樂行下月中接受紀律聆訊<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/&hellip;/5a68a428e603&hellip;/5a69b1f5e603832c6a41ecad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2F5a68a428e603%E2%80%A6%2F5a69b1f5e603832c6a41ecad&d=yZt%2BeEGgbzpLDrv0YPSTxY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5f53126e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/&hellip;/5a68a428e603&hellip;/5a69b1f5e603832c6a41ecad</a><br />\n<br />\nHKG報<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/hkgpaocom/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Fhkgpaocom%2F&d=yZt%2BeEGgbzpLDrv0YPSTxY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=bfea2698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/hkgpaocom/</a><br />\n<br />\nHKG報發起之所謂「支持錢大康」聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/&hellip;/1FAIpQLSczr0bq6h1cJsjJv_&hellip;/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2F1FAIpQLSczr0bq6h1cJsjJv_%E2%80%A6%2Fviewform&d=yZt%2BeEGgbzpLDrv0YPSTxY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c94660d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/&hellip;/1FAIpQLSczr0bq6h1cJsjJv_&hellip;/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\nNow TV對我們聯署行動的報道<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=251723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D251723&d=yZt%2BeEGgbzpLDrv0YPSTxY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=97987c86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D251723&h=64f35fd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=251723</a><br />\n<br />\n香港獨立媒體轉載我們的聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1054779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1054779&d=yZt%2BeEGgbzpLDrv0YPSTxY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=743ee1ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1054779&h=8a54a96b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1054779</a>"},{"pid":"2f846ef97518aca75c84cde22f77a8fa3ac6a281","tid":540642,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T16:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2fa0ebc2d0f4fcce571f265408b33de2bf8fec5","tid":540642,"uid":37584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T16:27:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d9d2229f212b428d9783a93eea6fe67d947fa3f7","tid":540642,"uid":12021,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:16:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fd44f9ba7be96a8ccd96d34889bc5045987085c","tid":540642,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"so 改返就當冇左件事架啦"},{"pid":"c365d254a63204f36ba0f2084494178e3e2b4b2b","tid":540642,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:20:02.000Z","msg":"搵記協啦"},{"pid":"e7b849368545098b46445a0e110c7141310c15ec","tid":540642,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:27:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵記協啦</blockquote><br />\n🙄"},{"pid":"6adcaf664350f6c268eb3727c7885677ef00a371","tid":540642,"uid":12021,"like":0