,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T20:26:51.000Z","msg":"投訴link<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=yZt%2BeEGgbzpLDrv0YPSTxY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0a184ecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n投訴內容，劣draft歡迎引用<br />\n<br />\n無線電視於1月25日的新聞報導中，將一個由網上傳媒發起的支持浸大校長聯署，說為浸大校友發起之聯署。<br />\n<br />\n查實當天另有一個由浸大校友發起的公開聯署，但目的卻是反對浸大校長在普通話試事件中的處事手法，無線電視的報導嚴重誤導公眾，本人希望貴局嚴正處理有關失實報導，並予以懲處。<br />\n<br />\n狂report<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b4f995ad37128f0077f34a96b5087815529907","tid":540642,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T20:37:35.000Z","msg":"無線電視於1月25日的新聞報導中，將一個由網上傳媒發起的支持浸大校長聯署，說為浸大校友發起之聯署。<br />\n<br />\n查實當天另有一個由浸大校友發起的公開聯署，但目的卻是反對浸大校長在普通話試事件中的處事手法，無線電視的報導試圖誤導公眾，<span style=\"color: red;\">失實內容令人覺得極為反感</span>，本人希望貴局嚴正處理，並予以懲處。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n改左做失實內容令人反感，費事咬唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41397745771f47e1199d6ff6c28d10367ff21b0f","tid":540642,"uid":166663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T00:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93894bc006037771d88da4bb34ec22da927eec38","tid":540642,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T00:35:10.000Z","msg":"通訊局見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d878fb328b9abe4f7b25d13994b166aabe0c238f","tid":540642,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T00:51:12.000Z","msg":"依家新聞部多咗批支那人喺度做<br />\n正常"},{"pid":"65d78cb3fe4ef93e331358f6df149cbb263822ae","tid":540642,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24b4f995ad37128f0077